Cactus Code Thorn TotalRestMass
Author(s)    : Tanja Bode <tanja.bode@physics.gatech.edu>
Maintainer(s): Tanja Bode <tanja.bode@physics.gatech.edu>
Licence      : GPL
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Purpose

Extremely basic thorn to sum over the rest mass in entire spacetime.
Implements simple summation of rho*dV*weight where weight is generally
just the CarpetWeight with modifications by AHMask to avoid the area 
inside the AH.
